/member/8/b/0/d/thumb_248495597.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/f/9/0/thumb_243796272.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/6/0/8/thumb_99574312.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/1/4/a/thumb_247317674.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/e/d/5/thumb_246400661.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/3/5/f/thumb_248493631.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/1/f/4/3/thumb_244688003.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/7/4/4/thumb_69790052.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/0/2/5/thumb_246256421.jpeg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"photo\"><img  src=\"//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/c/4/8/thumb_248491816.jpeg\" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style=\"line-height:16px\">WooCommerce is het meest populaire eCommerce platform ter wereld. Ook in Nederland begint het steeds meer grond te winnen, en daarom is het tijd voor de eerste community bijeenkomst! Op woensdagavond 26 augustus treffen we elkaar in het centrum van Utrecht.Restaurant/club Stairway To Heaven is zo vriendelijk geweest om ruimte voor ons beschikbaar &#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Utrecht-WooCommerce-Meetup/events/224374685/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<h3>WordPress Meetup Nijmegen September 2015</h3>\n<style type=\"text/css\">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: \" \"; clear: both; hei